WEBVTT

00:00:06.613 --> 00:00:07.693
(Previously)
Don't touch me.

00:00:08.566 --> 00:00:11.266
Can you not be mad at me, Erng?

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:14.284
Actually, by the time I
got home, I wasn't mad anymore.

00:00:14.285 --> 00:00:16.007
But can you do
me a favor next time?

00:00:16.008 --> 00:00:19.800
Just tell me nicely. I won't be mad
if you have a good reason.

00:00:20.466 --> 00:00:21.600
That means you're still mad.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:28.466
Tomorrow, before we go shopping,

00:00:28.866 --> 00:00:30.500
I want to stop by and see Bom first.

00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:37.166
I'm going to collect a debt.

00:00:37.900 --> 00:00:38.900
My wife...

00:00:39.766 --> 00:00:41.166
shifting gears like crazy,

00:00:41.366 --> 00:00:42.933
like some mobster delivering drugs.

00:00:48.166 --> 00:00:49.400
I'll handle it.

00:00:51.466 --> 00:00:52.666
Who wants to be a millionaire?

00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:55.166
- Erng.
- Me, of course!

00:01:00.566 --> 00:01:02.286
It's as beautiful as
the person who made it.

00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:05.300
Erng.

00:01:06.700 --> 00:01:07.700
Yes?

00:01:08.966 --> 00:01:10.286
You need to love this shop a lot.

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:23.700
And don't forget to love me too.

00:01:42.566 --> 00:01:44.066
If you're not happy being together,

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:46.000
then let's break up.

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:49.120
Don't stay and torture
each other like this.

00:01:50.266 --> 00:01:52.566
Can you act like we're in love?

00:01:55.366 --> 00:01:56.500
Can you do that?

00:01:59.966 --> 00:02:01.166
I'm not happy.

00:02:01.666 --> 00:02:03.466
So you shouldn't be happy either!

00:02:26.666 --> 00:02:28.800
Erng, I have a question.

00:02:30.700 --> 00:02:31.700
Hold on.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:33.000
Hey!

00:02:44.466 --> 00:02:46.476
Please, ask away. (He's imitating
how contestanst answer the question)

00:02:46.500 --> 00:02:49.500
This Miss Thailand
contestant is ready to answer.

00:02:51.733 --> 00:02:53.333
Do I have to clean the bathroom tonight?

00:02:54.366 --> 00:02:55.733
Thank you for the question.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:58.600
What kind of answer are you looking for?

00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:00.500
I'm hoping for "no."

00:03:02.566 --> 00:03:04.166
Congratulations!

00:03:04.933 --> 00:03:06.413
You don't have to clean the bathroom.

00:03:10.666 --> 00:03:12.133
Excellent answer!

00:03:13.966 --> 00:03:14.966
Wait a second.

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:21.900
Lean down a bit.

00:03:22.333 --> 00:03:24.400
It’s time to be crowned!

00:03:43.366 --> 00:03:44.366
Thank you.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.213
I spoil my boyfriend the most.

00:04:04.214 --> 00:04:06.235
No matter what he does,

00:04:06.637 --> 00:04:07.665
or how he is.

00:04:09.722 --> 00:04:11.268
His quirkiness...

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:15.281
I mean, his old-fashioned,

00:04:16.309 --> 00:04:18.523
made me fall in love with him from day one.

00:04:20.500 --> 00:04:22.262
Many people might think it's weird,

00:04:23.201 --> 00:04:24.418
but to me,

00:04:25.625 --> 00:04:27.577
it just makes me love him more every day.

00:04:28.838 --> 00:04:30.393
I want to see him smile

00:04:31.814 --> 00:04:33.499
and laugh like this forever.

00:05:00.933 --> 00:05:01.933
Hia.

00:05:03.766 --> 00:05:05.500
I think the shop sign looks really nice.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:07.733
At first, I didn't think I liked it.

00:05:09.533 --> 00:05:11.733
But the more I look
at it, the more I love it.

00:05:12.866 --> 00:05:14.900
And I think I'll love it
even more in the future.

00:05:21.366 --> 00:05:22.800
Let's make this place a home.

00:05:23.158 --> 00:05:24.458
Our home.

00:05:32.100 --> 00:05:33.666
Of course we're going to love it.

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:35.966
Our home is called "ChermChey."

00:05:38.100 --> 00:05:40.466
May this place always be
filled with joy and warmth.

00:05:51.166 --> 00:05:52.166
Hey, Hia.

00:05:52.933 --> 00:05:54.066
Is that the North Star?

00:05:54.466 --> 00:05:55.666
The North Star is out tonight.

00:05:56.133 --> 00:05:57.366
Oh god. My wife...

00:05:58.066 --> 00:05:59.733
That's a disco light.

00:06:10.100 --> 00:06:11.860
Why would the North
Star be inside the shop?

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:40.000
"Chermchey"
(Episode 7)

00:08:10.933 --> 00:08:11.542
Handsome,

00:08:11.542 --> 00:08:12.274
clean,

00:08:12.542 --> 00:08:14.034
with a solid six-pack

00:08:16.066 --> 00:08:17.066
and a V-line.

00:08:17.700 --> 00:08:19.333
Clenched from head to balls!

00:08:19.600 --> 00:08:21.076
Whoever gets him as a husband
(he's refer to himself in this context)

00:08:21.100 --> 00:08:22.100
will definitely be

00:08:22.466 --> 00:08:23.466
exhausted.

00:08:27.966 --> 00:08:29.200
Hia, put a shirt on.

00:08:31.733 --> 00:08:32.800
I admit you look great.

00:08:33.466 --> 00:08:34.466
Handsome,

00:08:34.866 --> 00:08:35.866
but weird.

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:39.400
Can you please act as good as you look?

00:08:51.366 --> 00:08:52.366
What the hell happened?

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:55.800
Whatever.

00:08:56.966 --> 00:08:57.966
Let's just open the shop.

00:08:58.466 --> 00:09:00.733
ChermChey is now open for business!

00:09:13.266 --> 00:09:14.266
Hia.

00:09:14.700 --> 00:09:15.700
Yeah?

00:09:15.866 --> 00:09:17.366
I'm going to go grab the ice.

00:09:18.300 --> 00:09:19.300
Grab it from where?

00:09:19.566 --> 00:09:20.566
Out back.

00:09:20.800 --> 00:09:22.120
The delivery truck arrived early,

00:09:22.300 --> 00:09:23.566
and Joy isn't here yet.

00:09:24.733 --> 00:09:25.866
I'll get it.

00:09:26.366 --> 00:09:27.926
You don't need to do the heavy lifting.

00:09:28.333 --> 00:09:29.333
Are you sure?

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:31.933
Then bring the invoice back too.

00:09:32.166 --> 00:09:33.266
Don't you dare forget it.

00:09:36.666 --> 00:09:37.859
Understood, ma'am.

00:09:38.306 --> 00:09:39.894
Don't you worry.

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:41.653
I definitely won't forget the invoice.

00:09:42.592 --> 00:09:43.966
Here, keep mopping.

00:09:47.945 --> 00:09:48.945
Hia.

00:09:56.666 --> 00:09:57.866
Give me some encouragement.

00:10:16.266 --> 00:10:18.132
Not like that.

00:10:18.133 --> 00:10:19.566
Then how?

00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:37.933
Ice delivery!

00:11:38.500 --> 00:11:39.600
Where should I put it?

00:11:46.766 --> 00:11:47.766
Just a moment, P'.

00:11:49.933 --> 00:11:50.933
Put it right there.

00:12:05.066 --> 00:12:06.066
Here.

00:12:06.565 --> 00:12:07.565
I made this for you

00:12:08.371 --> 00:12:09.479
so you won't lose it.

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:14.366
What kind of amulet is this?

00:12:17.866 --> 00:12:18.966
It's a Phra Khun Phaen.

00:12:20.333 --> 00:12:21.566
This one has powerful charm.

00:12:21.733 --> 00:12:22.733
Super potent!

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:26.000
Come here.

00:12:26.100 --> 00:12:27.333
Let me put it on you.

00:12:30.066 --> 00:12:31.066
Bless you.

00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:44.600
Do I need to say "Sathu" to this?
(Sathu is "Amen")

00:12:46.566 --> 00:12:47.886
No need for that with this model.

00:12:50.366 --> 00:12:51.500
Just a kiss is enough.

00:13:42.566 --> 00:13:43.566
What's up, Joy?

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:44.868
Hia, Mr. Erng!

00:13:44.869 --> 00:13:48.066
Customers are fighting out front.
They already broke a table!

00:13:50.866 --> 00:13:52.200
Drag them out of the shop!

00:13:53.533 --> 00:13:55.200
I don't welcome customers like that.

00:13:56.800 --> 00:13:57.600
Yeah.

00:13:57.733 --> 00:13:58.900
I'll go down myself.

00:14:06.500 --> 00:14:07.500
Erng!

00:14:07.733 --> 00:14:08.733
Calm down.

00:14:10.100 --> 00:14:11.100
With customers like that,

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:13.100
I can't stay calm!

00:14:14.533 --> 00:14:16.600
They're about to feel my Sailor Moon power!

00:14:27.358 --> 00:14:28.358
Damn it!

00:14:29.085 --> 00:14:30.520
What?

00:14:32.487 --> 00:14:33.783
Stay out of this!

00:14:40.766 --> 00:14:43.465
Go fight somewhere else!
Don't do this in my shop!

00:14:43.466 --> 00:14:44.614
Mind your own business!

00:14:49.533 --> 00:14:50.533
Please, guys.

00:14:50.700 --> 00:14:52.066
Go fight at another shop.

00:14:52.900 --> 00:14:53.900
Please?

00:14:55.500 --> 00:14:56.500
Oh!

00:14:56.933 --> 00:14:57.933
Please, guys!

00:15:01.300 --> 00:15:02.300
Yeah!

00:15:10.864 --> 00:15:12.550
I'll handle this.

00:15:12.551 --> 00:15:13.949
Hey, calm down!

00:15:13.950 --> 00:15:15.144
Hia, let me go!

00:15:15.145 --> 00:15:16.785
No way I'm letting you go.

00:15:16.786 --> 00:15:18.461
If I do, you'll just run after them.

00:15:25.500 --> 00:15:26.733
I've calmed down now.

00:15:28.466 --> 00:15:29.466
Let go.

00:15:29.866 --> 00:15:30.866
No.

00:15:32.300 --> 00:15:33.088
Joy!

00:15:33.088 --> 00:15:33.588
Yes?

00:15:33.588 --> 00:15:34.588
Clean up downstairs.

00:15:34.933 --> 00:15:35.933
Roger that!

00:15:36.103 --> 00:15:37.266
Let's go upstairs.

00:15:39.333 --> 00:15:40.133
Huh?

00:15:40.200 --> 00:15:42.066
My hands are itching to hit those guys.

00:16:06.966 --> 00:16:09.557
Damn, how much do you weigh?

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:11.609
My back is killing me.

00:16:14.100 --> 00:16:16.600
Don't you know you're not
supposed to ask a woman her weight?

00:16:19.166 --> 00:16:20.166
My bad.

00:16:22.866 --> 00:16:25.351
You're so weak. You can't
even carry your own wife.

00:16:25.375 --> 00:16:26.735
How are you going
to make a living?

00:16:26.900 --> 00:16:27.900
Huh?

00:16:29.400 --> 00:16:30.766
By having my wife support me.

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:32.900
See that? He's a real fighter.

00:16:33.133 --> 00:16:34.400
I couldn't even stop him.

00:16:35.166 --> 00:16:36.466
Did you get hurt anywhere?

00:16:38.266 --> 00:16:39.266
Just a little.

00:16:40.066 --> 00:16:41.333
I'm so small.

00:16:42.600 --> 00:16:43.600
Small?

00:16:46.166 --> 00:16:47.166
I saw what happened.

00:16:49.400 --> 00:16:50.400
I think

00:16:51.232 --> 00:16:53.632
they wanted to trash the shop
more than they wanted to fight.

00:17:10.401 --> 00:17:11.401
Damn it.

00:17:14.819 --> 00:17:15.819
Calm down.

00:17:16.145 --> 00:17:17.145
Leave me alone.

00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:15.240
I just wanted to ask

00:19:15.241 --> 00:19:16.925
if I could take over your shop.

00:19:17.685 --> 00:19:18.872
I want to do business.

00:19:18.873 --> 00:19:20.883
But if you see the shop

00:19:20.884 --> 00:19:22.743
and are okay with being partners,

00:19:23.816 --> 00:19:26.023
I'll draft a contract and
send it to you to sign.

00:19:27.400 --> 00:19:28.400
Deal.

00:19:28.708 --> 00:19:29.708
If you're in

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:31.000
I'm also in.

00:19:31.326 --> 00:19:32.345
Send it over.

00:19:38.400 --> 00:19:39.933
Where is my food list?

00:19:42.133 --> 00:19:43.133
Right here.

00:19:43.766 --> 00:19:45.533
Even though I've never run a bar,

00:19:45.866 --> 00:19:47.700
I've bought supplies for temple fairs.

00:19:53.600 --> 00:19:55.366
The menu is done. What do you think, Hia?

00:19:57.166 --> 00:19:58.166
I think it's good.

00:20:06.333 --> 00:20:09.266
ChermChey.

00:20:15.533 --> 00:20:17.100
Take a good look, Erng.

00:20:17.966 --> 00:20:20.733
Our shop is the hottest
spot in this neighborhood.

00:20:21.100 --> 00:20:22.966
ChermChey is now open for business!

00:22:56.166 --> 00:22:57.666
I'm giving you this amulet.

00:23:00.166 --> 00:23:01.300
Keep it with you.

00:23:02.933 --> 00:23:04.966
It'll keep you safe on your journey.

00:23:11.066 --> 00:23:12.766
Bow down to my chest.

00:23:16.133 --> 00:23:17.700
This amulet is special.

00:23:20.533 --> 00:23:22.300
I paid a fortune for it at an auction.

00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:31.000
You...

00:23:32.700 --> 00:23:35.133
really know how to take my breath away.

00:23:37.700 --> 00:23:39.666
I want you to remember this instead.

00:23:42.400 --> 00:23:43.933
You're more potent than any amulet.

00:23:50.566 --> 00:23:51.941
Then tonight...

00:23:52.791 --> 00:23:55.156
let me be your good luck charm.

00:23:58.500 --> 00:23:59.666
What are you thinking?

00:24:05.066 --> 00:24:06.066
I want to see it.

00:24:08.200 --> 00:24:09.200
See what?

00:24:12.666 --> 00:24:14.200
See you yield to me completely.

00:24:25.872 --> 00:24:26.923
My sweet boy.

00:24:54.133 --> 00:24:55.133
Yeah.

00:24:56.066 --> 00:24:57.066
Good.

00:24:57.933 --> 00:24:59.013
Keep your distance for now.

00:24:59.400 --> 00:25:00.400
Don't do anything yet.

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:02.866
Wait for my command before you act.

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:06.000
What are you doing?

00:25:07.133 --> 00:25:08.133
Talking to my family.

00:25:08.966 --> 00:25:10.566
Have you been awake long, Bom?

00:25:11.400 --> 00:25:13.700
Yeah, since you got out of bed.

00:25:15.100 --> 00:25:17.300
Go get dressed. Let's grab a bite.

00:25:17.533 --> 00:25:18.533
You're taking me?

00:25:18.600 --> 00:25:20.011
Yeah, want to go?

00:25:20.503 --> 00:25:21.983
You can pick any restaurant you like.

00:25:22.208 --> 00:25:23.208
My treat.

00:25:24.100 --> 00:25:25.454
What's gotten into you today?

00:25:25.767 --> 00:25:27.079
Why are you pampering me?

00:25:27.666 --> 00:25:29.100
Don't ruin the mood, okay?

00:25:29.766 --> 00:25:32.700
Just looking at my face
ruins your mood, doesn't it?

00:25:33.866 --> 00:25:34.866
A-ten.

00:25:34.933 --> 00:25:36.666
Yes, it's A-ten.

00:25:37.829 --> 00:25:39.006
Not P'Erng.

00:25:40.700 --> 00:25:42.000
What do you want, A-ten?

00:25:42.366 --> 00:25:43.366
When I'm with you,

00:25:43.666 --> 00:25:44.966
all you do is talk about Erng.

00:25:45.466 --> 00:25:46.826
And when I want to go back to him,

00:25:46.966 --> 00:25:47.966
you won't let me.

00:25:48.266 --> 00:25:49.626
You won't break up with me either.

00:25:49.733 --> 00:25:51.366
Being with you is pure torture.

00:25:51.533 --> 00:25:52.613
Do you regret it that much?

00:25:52.700 --> 00:25:53.700
For choosing me

00:25:54.800 --> 00:25:56.266
I just asked you out for a meal,

00:25:56.566 --> 00:25:57.800
and you had to pick a fight.

00:25:58.333 --> 00:25:59.500
Fine, don't eat then.

00:26:00.100 --> 00:26:00.900
You're so annoying.

00:26:00.933 --> 00:26:02.600
Fine, I'll stay right here and annoy you.

00:26:02.766 --> 00:26:04.133
Let's torture each other to death.

00:26:04.733 --> 00:26:05.733
Where are you going?

00:26:06.366 --> 00:26:07.866
Anywhere without you.

00:26:08.333 --> 00:26:09.500
Don't leave this room!

00:26:10.166 --> 00:26:11.166
P'Bom!

00:26:28.933 --> 00:26:30.413
You guys must really love each other.

00:26:31.366 --> 00:26:32.886
If we did, we wouldn't have broken up.

00:27:04.466 --> 00:27:06.588
Weekly horoscope for Sagittarius.

00:27:06.589 --> 00:27:10.287
If you have something special,
show it to the world this week.

00:27:10.288 --> 00:27:12.992
Let them know you've got what it takes.

00:27:12.993 --> 00:27:14.500
Show off. Don't miss out.

00:27:15.500 --> 00:27:18.020
Work might be a bit overwhelming lately.

00:27:18.021 --> 00:27:23.654
Take some time to rest, then
come back and have a blast at work.

00:27:24.056 --> 00:27:26.669
Finances: You're bound to make money.

00:27:26.670 --> 00:27:30.868
After some losses, business owners
will see unstoppable growth.

00:27:33.500 --> 00:27:36.792
Love: Singles will enjoy their freedom.

00:27:36.793 --> 00:27:40.759
Couples will face a test of true love.

00:27:40.760 --> 00:27:45.223
Face the problems together, and
your love will be smooth sailing.

00:27:45.224 --> 00:27:48.766
Watch out for a third party.
Catch them red-handed.

00:27:55.866 --> 00:27:56.866
- Erng.
- Oh!

00:27:57.333 --> 00:27:58.333
I just read horoscopes.

00:27:59.100 --> 00:28:00.660
It says you're going to have an affair.

00:28:00.800 --> 00:28:01.966
Are you cheating on me?

00:28:02.566 --> 00:28:03.566
What horoscope?

00:28:03.600 --> 00:28:04.900
The weekly horoscope.

00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:06.333
And what's your sign?

00:28:07.733 --> 00:28:08.853
A brown donkey.
(A Thai pun.)

00:28:10.100 --> 00:28:12.566
Do you want to meet the Grim Reaper early?

00:28:13.133 --> 00:28:14.133
Uh...

00:28:14.600 --> 00:28:15.866
Sagittarius. Sagittarius.

00:28:16.500 --> 00:28:17.500
I see.

00:28:18.366 --> 00:28:19.366
I'm dead meat.

00:28:20.400 --> 00:28:21.500
Reading horoscopes online?

00:28:21.900 --> 00:28:23.166
It popped up on LINE.

00:28:23.366 --> 00:28:24.533
So I clicked on it.

00:28:26.200 --> 00:28:27.700
It says you're having an affair.

00:28:28.300 --> 00:28:29.500
And you actually believe that?

00:28:32.300 --> 00:28:33.400
Well, is it true?

00:28:34.333 --> 00:28:37.200
We're glued to each other.
When would I have the time?

00:28:38.566 --> 00:28:41.566
I'm just worried because
my wife is so beautiful.

00:28:43.700 --> 00:28:44.700
Silly.

00:28:48.300 --> 00:28:49.466
I want to read mine too.

00:28:50.066 --> 00:28:51.166
Leo.

00:28:51.500 --> 00:28:52.500
Read it to me.

00:28:52.733 --> 00:28:53.733
Okay, fine.

00:28:54.533 --> 00:28:56.300
But don't take it too seriously.

00:28:56.533 --> 00:28:57.766
It's not that accurate.

00:28:58.300 --> 00:28:59.300
Wow.

00:28:59.700 --> 00:29:02.380
The guy who accused his partner
of cheating based on a horoscope...

00:29:03.300 --> 00:29:05.260
is lecturing me about
not taking it seriously?

00:29:06.100 --> 00:29:08.071
I was just teasing you.

00:29:08.072 --> 00:29:09.072
Swear?

00:29:10.400 --> 00:29:11.200
Yeah.

00:29:11.300 --> 00:29:12.300
I believe in fate.

00:29:12.733 --> 00:29:14.000
Are you happy now, sweetheart?

00:29:17.366 --> 00:29:18.500
Leo.

00:29:19.666 --> 00:29:22.333
Forgiveness is the best revenge.

00:29:22.966 --> 00:29:23.966
Don't miss out.

00:29:24.533 --> 00:29:25.533
Work:

00:29:25.700 --> 00:29:27.400
Those close to you will support you.

00:29:27.766 --> 00:29:29.166
There might be some issues at work,

00:29:29.366 --> 00:29:32.066
but they will lead you to
a great partner and friend.

00:29:33.100 --> 00:29:34.100
Finances:

00:29:34.378 --> 00:29:35.928
You'll make a lot but won't spend it.

00:29:36.375 --> 00:29:40.755
Savings will grow. Someone you trust
is managing your income and expenses.

00:29:41.694 --> 00:29:42.769
Love:

00:29:43.350 --> 00:29:44.825
Singles are highly attractive.

00:29:45.987 --> 00:29:47.278
Couples:

00:29:47.546 --> 00:29:48.680
A little touch...

00:29:48.681 --> 00:29:50.913
will spark a wild fire.

00:29:52.500 --> 00:29:54.900
Keep charming your partner regularly.

00:29:55.266 --> 00:29:56.266
Don't miss out.

00:29:57.133 --> 00:29:58.300
You've been warned.

00:30:00.166 --> 00:30:01.700
Spark a wild fire, huh?

00:30:02.133 --> 00:30:02.800
Go.

00:30:02.800 --> 00:30:03.800
Go take a shower.

00:30:04.400 --> 00:30:05.400
Get cleaned up.

00:30:06.300 --> 00:30:07.933
And then we can spark some fire.

00:30:10.533 --> 00:30:13.200
You always turn everything
into something dirty.

00:30:17.533 --> 00:30:19.400
We haven't been very exciting lately.

00:30:19.866 --> 00:30:21.466
I hugged you this morning,

00:30:22.400 --> 00:30:23.480
but you didn't hug me back.

00:30:23.933 --> 00:30:26.733
You just lay there making lazy noises.

00:30:34.366 --> 00:30:36.666
Don't try to nibble on me while I'm asleep.

00:31:31.166 --> 00:31:31.966
Yeah.

00:31:32.166 --> 00:31:32.966
Do we look alike?

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:33.800
Exactly alike.

00:31:33.966 --> 00:31:34.606
Hm?

00:31:34.607 --> 00:31:35.825
This is Moo Deng.

00:31:35.826 --> 00:31:36.326
Hm?

00:31:36.326 --> 00:31:37.326
And this...

00:31:37.800 --> 00:31:38.842
is Erng Deng.
(Deng means bouncing in Thai)

00:31:38.866 --> 00:31:40.400
See?

00:31:42.100 --> 00:31:43.166
I'm not sleepy yet.

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.000
Hmm.

00:31:46.483 --> 00:31:47.900
Should we find something to do?

00:31:51.166 --> 00:31:52.166
Watch a movie?

00:31:52.354 --> 00:31:53.535
Play games?

00:31:54.366 --> 00:31:55.366
Sure.

00:31:55.500 --> 00:31:56.500
Why not?

00:31:56.600 --> 00:31:57.600
Then...

00:31:57.905 --> 00:31:59.660
I'll go grab some snacks and beer.

00:32:00.420 --> 00:32:01.540
I know you get hungry often.

00:32:02.366 --> 00:32:04.792
Yes, Erng Erng gets hungry often.

00:32:05.600 --> 00:32:07.500
But not as hungry as you.

00:32:18.812 --> 00:32:19.812
Are you sick?

00:32:20.166 --> 00:32:21.266
Are you feeling okay?

00:32:27.933 --> 00:32:30.366
It's my turn. You can't kiss me!

00:32:37.533 --> 00:32:38.533
Go on.

00:32:43.900 --> 00:32:44.900
What is wrong with you?

00:32:46.666 --> 00:32:48.166
What's gotten into you?

00:32:48.366 --> 00:32:49.366
I'm just in love.

00:32:49.600 --> 00:32:50.600
My heart is full of love.

00:32:50.800 --> 00:32:51.800
What can I do?

00:32:53.200 --> 00:32:54.200
Go quickly.

00:32:55.200 --> 00:32:56.200
Mmh.

00:33:04.066 --> 00:33:04.643
Right?

00:33:04.643 --> 00:33:05.643
No.

00:33:05.933 --> 00:33:07.430
Go grab the stuff first.

00:33:08.066 --> 00:33:09.733
Be a good boy.

00:33:11.933 --> 00:33:13.100
I am being good.

00:33:20.566 --> 00:33:21.736
Where are the snacks?

00:33:21.737 --> 00:33:22.737
One more.

00:33:25.774 --> 00:33:26.774
Hia.

00:33:27.915 --> 00:33:28.916
I'm going.

00:33:33.333 --> 00:33:34.333
Hurry up.

00:33:34.866 --> 00:33:35.866
I'm craving it.

00:33:36.200 --> 00:33:37.200
I want you.

00:33:38.000 --> 00:33:39.100
You little hippo.

00:33:41.700 --> 00:33:42.866
You're the hippo.

00:33:46.100 --> 00:33:47.566
Who looks more like it?

00:34:04.266 --> 00:34:05.297
Who's that?

00:34:07.264 --> 00:34:09.980
A thief trying to break into my shop?

00:34:11.098 --> 00:34:13.919
That horoscope was actually spot on.

00:34:13.920 --> 00:34:17.847
Something special really
did come my way today.

00:34:34.400 --> 00:34:35.200
Hey.

00:34:35.366 --> 00:34:35.887
Shit!

00:34:35.888 --> 00:34:37.266
Intha, how did you get here?

00:34:37.666 --> 00:34:38.900
How do you know my name?

00:35:00.900 --> 00:35:01.900
Ow!

00:35:02.166 --> 00:35:03.166
Thief!

00:35:09.066 --> 00:35:10.184
Let him go.

00:35:10.185 --> 00:35:12.300
Let's finish the job so we can get paid.

00:35:13.266 --> 00:35:16.000
Fine. Keep watch. I'll handle this.

00:35:17.133 --> 00:35:19.900
He only said to teach him a
lesson. Just trash the storefront.

00:35:21.100 --> 00:35:22.361
Yeah, I know.

00:35:22.362 --> 00:35:23.362
Go.

00:35:43.402 --> 00:35:45.344
Whoa, calm down, man!

00:35:46.104 --> 00:35:47.765
I'm going to kill you!

00:35:47.766 --> 00:35:48.766
I'm sorry, P'.

00:36:12.066 --> 00:36:13.066
You...

00:36:13.800 --> 00:36:15.880
You're the guy who started
a fight at my bar before.

00:36:16.933 --> 00:36:17.933
I'm sorry.

00:36:18.500 --> 00:36:19.700
I won't do it again.

00:36:19.966 --> 00:36:20.966
I'm sorry.

00:36:22.566 --> 00:36:23.726
What were you planning to do?

00:36:25.266 --> 00:36:26.066
Answer me!

00:36:26.133 --> 00:36:27.742
If you don't answer, I'll kill
you and bury you right here.

00:36:27.766 --> 00:36:29.400
Someone... someone hired me.

00:36:29.766 --> 00:36:31.733
Someone hired me, man.

00:36:46.900 --> 00:36:50.900
I think they wanted to trash
the bar, not just start a fight.

00:37:03.466 --> 00:37:04.733
- Bom.
- A-tens.

00:37:04.900 --> 00:37:05.900
Why did you do this?

00:37:06.066 --> 00:37:07.600
I told you I was breaking up with you.

00:37:08.066 --> 00:37:09.066
I'm not breaking up.

00:37:09.200 --> 00:37:11.133
If we break up, you'll
just go back to Erng.

00:37:11.366 --> 00:37:13.133
Yeah, because Erng is better than you!

00:37:20.566 --> 00:37:21.566
Who hired you?

00:37:22.366 --> 00:37:23.366
Mr...

00:37:23.733 --> 00:37:24.733
Mr...

00:37:24.966 --> 00:37:25.766
Mr. Who?

00:37:25.800 --> 00:37:27.100
Mr... Mr. A-tens.

00:37:27.500 --> 00:37:30.533
Mr. A-tens hired me.

00:37:31.933 --> 00:37:33.200
- Bom.
- A-tens.

00:37:33.316 --> 00:37:34.666
Why did you do this?

00:37:56.000 --> 00:37:57.600
Bom wanted to break up with me.

00:37:58.300 --> 00:38:00.066
He said he was going back to you.

00:38:39.566 --> 00:38:40.566
Erng!

00:38:41.800 --> 00:38:42.600
Erng!

00:38:42.766 --> 00:38:44.000
Please be okay.

00:38:50.266 --> 00:38:51.266
Let's go, hurry!

00:38:51.566 --> 00:38:52.566
Hurry!

00:39:38.000 --> 00:39:41.566
I love the time after the
bar closes. It's so quiet.

00:39:42.700 --> 00:39:44.680
Just me and Hia.

00:39:44.681 --> 00:39:46.222
Cleaning up the place together.

00:39:46.223 --> 00:39:48.693
Sweeping the floor, washing glasses.

00:39:48.694 --> 00:39:50.800
It feels more like home than a bar.

00:39:51.500 --> 00:39:52.784
I like it too.

00:39:52.785 --> 00:39:55.138
Especially when Erng starts being dramatic.

00:39:55.496 --> 00:39:56.781
I'm exhausted,

00:39:57.228 --> 00:39:59.138
but he's so damn cute.

00:40:00.900 --> 00:40:03.586
At first, I didn't really
like the bar's sign.

00:40:03.587 --> 00:40:05.765
I thought it was as tacky as its name.

00:40:06.078 --> 00:40:07.792
But looking at it every day,

00:40:07.793 --> 00:40:10.714
seeing Hia help put it
up and set things up,

00:40:12.011 --> 00:40:14.104
building this place together...

00:40:14.105 --> 00:40:17.492
I've grown to love it more and more.

00:40:18.400 --> 00:40:19.700
When Erng said,

00:40:20.866 --> 00:40:22.200
"Let's make this place our home,"

00:40:23.366 --> 00:40:24.733
I was so incredibly happy.

00:40:25.600 --> 00:40:27.300
But I didn't dare say it out loud.

00:40:29.133 --> 00:40:31.053
I could only tease him to
hide my embarrassment.

00:40:32.600 --> 00:40:35.055
Hia In dresses so weirdly.

00:40:35.056 --> 00:40:38.023
Like a mix between a monk and a biker boy.

00:40:38.024 --> 00:40:41.558
Wearing an amulet with a
low-cut shirt like it's nothing.

00:40:43.972 --> 00:40:47.934
But strangely, the more I look,
the more handsome he gets.

00:40:51.566 --> 00:40:53.566
And Erng always
flirts without realizing it.

00:40:56.500 --> 00:40:58.800
It's like he's trying to make
me head over heels for him.

00:40:59.766 --> 00:41:01.844
My favorite part of the day

00:41:01.845 --> 00:41:04.460
is having a meal with Hia.

00:41:04.461 --> 00:41:10.531
Little things like fish kidney curry, the
bottle opener, or serving food to each other...

00:41:10.532 --> 00:41:12.640
It feels so warm, it's almost scary.

00:41:12.641 --> 00:41:15.300
It's like I'm getting
addicted to this life.

00:41:16.566 --> 00:41:18.200
I love watching Erng eat.

00:41:19.366 --> 00:41:21.646
The way his eyes light up
when he eats his favorite food.

00:41:21.966 --> 00:41:22.966
He's just like a kid.

00:41:24.200 --> 00:41:26.866
And when I put the bottle
opener necklace on him,

00:41:28.000 --> 00:41:30.466
his smile made me want
to give him my whole life.

00:41:32.733 --> 00:41:34.644
But happiness never lasts long.

00:41:34.645 --> 00:41:39.156
Customers fought, tables
broke, and the bar was trashed.

00:41:39.157 --> 00:41:41.533
And I lost my temper completely.

00:41:43.400 --> 00:41:45.733
When I saw Erng charging
at someone with a chair,

00:41:46.200 --> 00:41:47.466
I was genuinely shocked.

00:41:48.566 --> 00:41:49.766
Like a stubborn kitten

00:41:50.500 --> 00:41:52.260
turning into a tiger in
a matter of seconds.

00:41:54.366 --> 00:41:56.314
Hia In always treats me like a kid,

00:41:56.315 --> 00:42:00.426
when I was just angry on behalf of our bar.

00:42:00.427 --> 00:42:04.300
But when he carried me to
the room, I secretly felt good.

00:42:05.733 --> 00:42:06.733
I was scared.

00:42:07.600 --> 00:42:08.733
Not of those people,

00:42:09.900 --> 00:42:11.266
but that Erng would get hurt.

00:42:12.200 --> 00:42:14.133
Scared he'd ruin himself
over his temper again.

00:42:16.200 --> 00:42:20.100
That night, I thought the chaos was over.

00:42:21.400 --> 00:42:23.066
But in reality, it had only just begun.

00:42:24.533 --> 00:42:26.400
Some people get hurt
and choose to walk away.

00:42:27.466 --> 00:42:30.966
But others choose to do
whatever it takes instead.

00:42:33.066 --> 00:42:34.706
I was just checking my horoscope for fun.

00:42:35.166 --> 00:42:36.700
But when I read about a third party,

00:42:37.333 --> 00:42:38.500
I couldn't help but worry.

00:42:39.000 --> 00:42:40.966
Because I've fallen way too hard for Erng.

00:42:42.000 --> 00:42:44.166
I love the moments
when it's just the two of us.

00:42:45.133 --> 00:42:46.133
No customers.

00:42:46.500 --> 00:42:47.800
No loud music.

00:42:48.933 --> 00:42:50.700
Just Hia hugging me from behind.

00:42:52.066 --> 00:42:53.594
It makes me feel like

00:42:54.220 --> 00:42:58.933
no matter how chaotic the outside world is,
I still have a place to return to.

00:43:00.700 --> 00:43:04.172
And that night, everything
changed once again.

00:43:04.173 --> 00:43:06.152
I saw the intruders on the security camera.

00:43:06.867 --> 00:43:09.581
At first, I thought they
were just here to steal.

00:43:10.133 --> 00:43:11.933
But when they called out my name,

00:43:13.066 --> 00:43:15.700
I knew right away this
was something bigger.

00:43:16.266 --> 00:43:19.891
And I had no idea that
while Hia was chasing them,

00:43:19.892 --> 00:43:22.200
our bar was being set on fire.

00:43:22.766 --> 00:43:23.766
When I saw the fire,

00:43:24.700 --> 00:43:26.366
my heart almost stopped.

00:43:27.133 --> 00:43:28.966
I didn't even care about the bar first.

00:43:29.966 --> 00:43:31.000
I only cared about Erng.

00:43:33.066 --> 00:43:34.786
At that moment, I only asked for one thing.

00:43:35.366 --> 00:43:36.566
Please let him still be there.

00:43:37.500 --> 00:43:38.700
Please let Erng be safe.

00:43:39.166 --> 00:43:40.733
Because if I lost him,

00:43:41.900 --> 00:43:43.400
I'd truly have nothing left.

00:43:47.933 --> 00:43:50.133
(Next Episode)
I don't want to talk to anyone right now.

00:43:53.866 --> 00:43:55.100
My heart hurts too much.

00:43:58.333 --> 00:44:00.000
About burning down your bar...

00:44:01.133 --> 00:44:03.366
I don't really feel that guilty about it.

00:44:03.966 --> 00:44:05.606
I'm just apologizing to get it over with.

00:44:09.400 --> 00:44:13.366
Hia, are you tired of me
being such a troublemaker?